abstract: The Denver Broncos announced yesterday that their star runner, Otis Armstrong, has a birth-related spinal condition and would risk permanent paralysis if he were to continue playing football. After Armstrong was placed on the injured-reserve list, the Broncos' orthopedist said: "Otis Armstrong should never play football again."
